&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;You will partner&amp;nbsp;across&amp;nbsp;Finance, Human Resources, and external service providers to support payroll, audits, financial reporting, and process improvements. This role offers broad exposure across the accounting function and the opportunity to help build scalable processes that support Alpha-9&#39;s continued growth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:300}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
